The paper discusses security technologies for wireless sensor networks, which is a topic that falls under the computer science sub-categories of Cryptography and Security (cs.CR), Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI), Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC), Software Engineering (cs.SE), and Systems and Control (cs.SY). However, since the focus of the paper is on security, cs.CR and cs.NI are the most likely sub-categories.
